TextBody:
Hi Mark,

Thank you for reaching out.

For Windows clients, you can use the following command/script: 
msiexec.exe /x "path_to_msi" ADMIN_PASSWORD_0="your_uninstall_password" REBOOT=ReallySuppress REMOVE_PROP=1 /qn

If you have any other questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.

Best Regards,
Iosif Muntean| Technical Support Engineer
Endpoint Protector by CoSoSys, now part of Netwrix
DLP | Device Control | Content Aware Protection | eDiscovery | Enforced Encryption
